PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1400 - PICLORAM) by setting maximum limits on residues of this product (a) resulting from its use as an herbicide on barley and wheat; or (b) which may remain in the fat, meat and organs of certain animals and their by-products, and in milk.
